## Cart component

The **Cart component** is available as part of the [User bar (VX) widget.](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_user-bar-vx-widget_.md)

The component can be placed on your site header in order to be easily accessible at all times. Its required if you utilize the Cart functionality in Voxel.

The styling can be customized under [Popup Styles](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_popup-kit-vx-widget_.md)

No other configuration required.
